## Self-Restart

NEVER run `pm2 restart` directly. That kills the process mid-handler and causes a crash loop.

Standard restart:
```bash
nohup bash {{PROJECT_ROOT}}/scripts/restart.sh {{BOT_NAME}} &>/dev/null &
```

Build restart (with ack message to {{OWNER_NAME}}):
```bash
node {{PROJECT_ROOT}}/dist/save-restart-context-cli.js \
  "internal summary" "message {{OWNER_NAME}} sees" \
  --files=changed.ts --status=clean --phase="Phase name"
nohup bash {{PROJECT_ROOT}}/scripts/restart.sh {{BOT_NAME}} &>/dev/null &
```

